SpaceX Rocket Explodes at Launchpad in Cape Canaveral,"The explosion was particularly painful news for Facebook�۪s chief executive, Mark Zuckerberg, who is touring Kenya, promoting a program reliant on the satellite, known as Amos-6, with entrepreneurs in the country. He had promised them connectivity.

